step_description: Set aside 8 gal DI water in two clean buckets (4 gal per bucket).
Add CHEM - DOW PG Carbo Wax 300.
Dissolve DYE-KEYACID TARTRAZINE 801-023 into a bucket with 4gal of DI water.
Dissolve DYE-PYLAM AMARANTH RED LX-9944 into a bucket with 4gal of DI water.
Add DYE-PYLAM AMARANTH RED LX-9944 water mixture.
Ensure that the DI water pump is turned off.
Add MetalGuard A 81 at 1 gallon per minute
Add MetalGuard A 81 at 1 gallon per minute
Add MetalGuard A 81 at 1 gallon per minute
Charge vessel with LPA / Mineral Spirits.
Charge vessel with IPA - Make sure tote cage is grounded properly
Charge vessel with LPA / Mineral Spirits.
Charge tote with Barnacle Remover blend.
Charge vessel with DI water: DO NOT USE DI TANK. DIRECT FEED ONLY.
Charge vessel with DI water: DO NOT USE DI TANK. DIRECT FEED ONLY.
Pour 200 gallons of DI water into the Kelzan mix vessel.
Charge the main mix vessel with DI Water.
Add canola oil to the tote.
Charge vessel with Conoco Ultra S8
Charge vessel with Conoco Ultra S8
Charge vessel with Conoco Ultra S8
Charge vessel with LPA / Mineral Spirits.
